node.text: Two weeks ago we went on the Run To Ibiza with our friends at Roger Dubuis: 1400+ km of driving the Aventador S in a supercar convoy through Portugal and Spain, ending up in Ibiza for closing weekend. Here is a quick 1 minute recap of an unforgettable trip.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Good Life Inc. in Geneva, Switzerland with @fsgeneva. May be an image of chandelier and indoor.

node.text: The lovely lobby of the Four Seasons Hotel des Bergues. Did you know that this historic property dates from 1834 and was the first ever luxury hotel in Geneva? #thegoodlifeinc

node.text: The Eisbach is a small, 2-kilometre-long, man-made river in Munich. It features a wave on one section which is popular among river surfers. This guy was killing it yesterday 🏄‍♂️ #thegoodlifeinc
